        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This oak branch grows leaves in spring that change color in autumn and shed in winter. While wielding it, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to checks to identify plants and fungi.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrips</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Tanglefoot]</em></li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Shillelagh]</em> (can target the verdant staff)</li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Barkskin]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Entangle]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Shape Wood]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Tree Shape]</em></li>\n<li><strong>3rd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Wall of Thorns]</em></li>\n<li><strong>4th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Barkskin]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Speak with Plants]</em></li>\n<li><strong>5th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Plant Form]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Wall of Thorns]</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>"
